==Transportation==
The fastest way to get there is by casting [[Ghorrock Teleport]] or using its [[Ghorrock teleport (tablet)|magic tablet]] equivalent. Alternatively, a [[burning amulet]] can teleport players to the entrance of the [[Lava Maze]]; run west from there. Alternatively, players with the hard [[Wilderness Diary]] completed and a [[Obelisk (Construction)|POH obelisk]] can select the level 44 Wilderness teleport.

